title: Call of duty black ops mac
description:
This is cod black ops 1 for the mac.
Note: This is the native mac version no wineskin.
I'm sorry to say it but multiplayer does not work :(
You can play combat training, single player campaign and solo zombies.
One more thing its going to ask to log in with game center please do that or els you wont even be able to play solo zombies or combat training. 
Don't forget to seed.
